data.description:
This  home boasts of a kitchen, dining combo and kitchen Livingroom combo. There is a space for a wood stove, pellet, etc in livingroom.  There are 3 nice sized Bedrooms with a full bath and laundry with basement access.
Garage could entertain 4 vehicles and has a workshop area.
Hot water tank is 1 yr old, some newer windows. New filtration system.  Private backyard.   Home is where is, as is.  Any home inspection will be responsibility of the buyers for any repairs if needed.  Must show proof of funds and buyer attorney.
